HEADWORD: Somedeal
<hw>Some"deal`</hw> <pr>(s⟦ucr⟧m"d⟦emac⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<def>In some degree; somewhat.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>sumdel</asp>, <asp>sumdeale</asp>, and <asp>sumdele</asp>.]</altsp>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧She was <xex>somedeal</xex> deaf.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou lackest <qex>somedeal</qex> their delight.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Somehow</ent>⟦br⟧
